rder-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: =
solid; background-color: #ccc;">Sam Altman will</a>:</p>
<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Days before OpenAI demonstrated its new, flirt=
y voice assistant last week, the actress Scarlett Johansson said, Sam Altma=
n, the company=E2=80=99s chief executive, called her agent and asked that s=
he consider licensing her voice for a virtual assistant.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">It was his second request to the actress in th=
e past year, [Ms. Johansson] said in a statement on Monday, adding that the=
 reply both times was no.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Despite those refusals, Ms. Johansson said, Op=
enAI used a voice that sounded =E2=80=9Ceerily similar to mine.=E2=80=9D Sh=
e has hired a lawyer and asked OpenAI to stop using a voice it called =E2=
=80=9CSky.=E2=80=9D</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">OpenAI suspended its release of =E2=80=9CSky=
=E2=80=9D over the weekend. The company said in a blog post on Sunday that =
=E2=80=9CAI voices should not deliberately mimic a celebrity=E2=80=99s dist=
inctive voice =E2=80=94 Sky=E2=80=99s voice is not an imitation of Scarlett=
 Johansson but belongs to a different professional actress using her own na=
tural speaking voice.=E2=80=9D=C2=A0</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">For Ms. Johansson, the episode has been a surr=
eal case of life-imitating art. In 2013, she provided the voice for an A.I.=
