<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Last week, Mr. Altman appeared to nod to the s=
imilarity between OpenAI=E2=80=99s virtual assistant and the film in a post=
 on X with the single word =E2=80=9Cher.=E2=80=9D</p>
</blockquote>
